|---|---|
| Background | `#F0FDFA` (teal-50) |
| Surface (card) | `#FFFFFF` |
| Primary | `#0D9488` (teal-600) |
| Primary dark | `#0F766E` (teal-700) |
| Clinical accent | `#059669` (emerald-600) |
| Live call accent | `#F59E0B` (amber-500) — active call state, pulsing ring |
| Escalation/alert | `#EF4444` (red-500) |
| Text primary | `#1E293B` (slate-800) |
| Text secondary | `#64748B` (slate-500) |
